{"tid":757274,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"追你嗰時當你係寶","createTime":"2018-07-26T16:48:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-27T01:22:37.000Z","uid":155531,"like":50,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"f95134dbc3698a95d65633bb667790cbf6d597d3","tid":757274,"uid":155531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T16:48:54.000Z","msg":"追我嗰陣好小事都會記得一清二楚<br />\n追到就懶懶閒<br />\n<br />\n成日都唔講去邊 又唔會關心我向邊<br />\n我知你返工忙唔揾我好正常<br />\n但收工都唔會覆多啲機<br />\n<br />\n已經成日同自己講唔好同人地比較<br />\n但見到朋友有男朋友接下收工<br />\n夜返男朋友會關心 話返屋企小心啲<br />\n返到打比佢之類好關心自己嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n我都係會羡慕嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好辛苦，完全唔似拍拖<br />\n不如自己一個仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1907cdb5071aa3afb123b4f77a2cbfb49b6d4e61","tid":757274,"uid":27793,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T16:52:09.000Z","msg":"保持自信<br />\n你有你既生活<br />\n有時撒下嬌<br />\n有時自己可以獨立做自己鍾意既嘢<br />\n<br />\n佢會r返你轉頭<br />\n<br />\n試過"},{"pid":"babf1ce4b2bfa6951aede349a50944ef00384e6d","tid":757274,"uid":27793,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T16:54:12.000Z","msg":"點解追你個陣對你咁用心？<br />\n<br />\n因為佢要同你競爭你<br />\n我搵工都係<br />\n超級積極<br />\n連公司背景都熟埋<br />\n<br />\n做左一年就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好正常<br />\n<br />\n都幾多男人係咁<br />\n除非佢成日無嘢做<br />\n9成時間諗女人/女友"},{"pid":"0a1d375e7e72c830ef7766e0601d65cf50ed808b","tid":757274,"uid":27793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T16:54:41.000Z","msg":"*同其他人競爭你"},{"pid":"2043c6d9241b3d548d607c0e019864270b7cb74b","tid":757274,"uid":18568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T16:56:03.000Z","msg":"同我拍拖囉<br />\n我唔會咁對你"},{"pid":"fdacbec685c16d501012ed1d1f6e8fe5b0f19b31","tid":757274,"uid":165024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T16:56:57.000Z","msg":"男人重視結果 女人重視過程"},{"pid":"c2c07066a77af5a47230a45850ffeff09fdc9b8f","tid":757274,"uid":155531,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1907cdb5071aa3afb123b4f77a2cbfb49b6d4e61","tid":757274,"uid":27793,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T16:52:09.000Z","msg":"保持自信<br />\n你有你既生活<br />\n有時撒下嬌<br />\n有時自己可以獨立做自己鍾意既嘢<br />\n<br />\n佢會r返你轉頭<br />\n<br />\n試過"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T16:57:17.000Z","msg":"成日去邊又唔講<br />\n佢講得越少我又唔想講<br />\n<br />\n感覺完全唔似男女朋友 或者仲衰過做朋友"},{"pid":"8460e849e79ff41724fabec485b97f9dcd121402","tid":757274,"uid":190066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T16:57:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1be3bacc769802a5ab13013d6b5d7f4beffc00a3","tid":757274,"uid":155531,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fdacbec685c16d501012ed1d1f6e8fe5b0f19b31","tid":757274,"uid":165024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T16:56:57.000Z","msg":"男人重視結果 女人重視過程"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T16:59:10.000Z","msg":"女朋友只係名銜"},{"pid":"5eba6494d63bf243a2eed35973c74c184f613240","tid":757274,"uid":155531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8460e849e79ff41724fabec485b97f9dcd121402","tid":757274,"uid":190066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T16:57:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T16:59:58.000Z","msg":"咁可以點"},{"pid":"db4238bc45e2cc6e79f53c63bd356b254b3e277a","tid":757274,"uid":9394,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T17:01:43.000Z","msg":"可以試下執靚啲 比啲新鮮感佢<br />\n外表其實都重要"},{"pid":"074f6afacc86e44b6074b2dc514f718a0e9a08e9","tid":757274,"uid":55623,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T17:05:32.000Z","msg":"唔好再圍住佢轉 要有多啲自己嘅生活<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同我自己講嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0823c6b683ecf1134b35b92fae0076bc708f53e","tid":757274,"uid":36692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1